artist: Master E.S.; Max Geisberg; Published by Bruno Cassirer
description: Second installment of (once) bound volume of reproductions by Master E.S. given by Miss F. January beginning in 1923 with notation in print registry to be reported as anonymous. This installment is complete and is numbered P.6,953 1/41 to P.6,953 41/41. There are mulitple images on many of the pages. Images preceeded by a "List of Figures" (Verzeichnis der Abbildungen).
title: Die Kupferstiche Des Meisters E.S.
